Class Cities

  • java.lang.Object
    • game.Cities

  • public class Cities
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    vsh33 Cities is a class that holds all the attributes of a city the user has to complete. Each city has four locations; villains lair, powerup den, hospital, shop. Cities class randomly assigns locations for the user to navigate through
